protocol.name: P-G5535-1
protocol.text: This was a control sample and was harvested under the biosample growth conditions.

protocol.name: P-G5535-2
protocol.text: Flats containing the plants were transferred to 4 degree celsius under continuous light (~25 umol m-2 s-1) and tissue samples were harvested after 1 hour at 4 degree celsius

protocol.name: P-G5535-3
protocol.text: Flats containing the plants were transferred to 4 degree celsius under continuous light (~25 umol m-2 s-1) and tissue samples were harvested after 24 hours at 4 degree celsius

protocol.name: P-G5535-4
protocol.text: Flats containing the plants were transferred to 4 degree celsius under continuous light (~25 umol m-2 s-1) and tissue samples were harvested after 7 days at 4 degree celsius
